OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCustomers warned of energy 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbill rises from April      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy firms will begin writing to     
OL,6, customers within days to warn them of  
OL,7, bill increases from the start of April.
OL,9,FFirms have to give customers reasonable
OL,10,Fnotice of price increases or changes   
OL,11,Fthat will leave them worse off,        
OL,12,Faccording to Citizens Advice.          
OL,14,FTypical household energy bills are set 
OL,15,Fto rise to #3,000 per year from April. 
OL,17,FThe BBC understands the government is  
OL,18,Freviewing the level of energy support  
OL,19,Famid calls by campaigners for help to  
OL,20,Fbe maintained to prevent bills rising. 
